}}'''''The Snow Queen''''' is a [[interactive fiction]] game created by Irish developer [[Silver Sisterhood|St. Bride's School]] and published by Mosaic Publishing for the [[Commodore 64]] and [[ZX Spectrum]] in 1985. It is based on the 1844 fairy tale "[[The Snow Queen]]" by [[Hans Christian Andersen]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sincuser.f9.co.uk/044/advent.htm|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120131205849/http://www.sincuser.f9.co.uk/044/advent.htm|title=Sinclair User 44 - Adventure|archivedate=31 January 2012|work=f9.co.uk}}</ref>

==Plot==
The story closely follows the story of "The Snow Queen" by Hans Christian Andersen. The player takes on the role of Gerda, whose friend Kay has been kidnapped by the Snow Queen and taken to her home in the mountains. Gerda must attempt to rescue her friend.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://archive.org/details/computer-and-videogames-052/page/n76/mode/1up?view=theater|title = Computer and Videogames Magazine Issue 052|date = February 1986}}</ref>

==Reception==
''The Snow Queen'' was generally moderately well received, including review scores of 60% from ''[[Computer Gamer]]'',<ref>{{cite web|url=https://archive.org/stream/Computer_Gamer_Issue_09_1985-12_Argus_Press_GB#page/n59/mode/1up/|title=Computer Gamer - Issue 09 (1985-12)(Argus Press)(GB)|work=archive.org|date=December 1985}}</ref> 21/30 from ''[[Computer & Video Games]]'',<ref>{{cite web|url=https://archive.org/stream/computer-and-videogames-052/ComputerAndVideoGames_052_Feb_1986#page/n76/mode/1up/|title=Computer and Videogames Magazine Issue 052|work=archive.org|date=February 1986}}</ref> 7/10 from ''[[Crash (magazine)|Crash]]'',<ref>{{cite web|url=https://archive.org/stream/Crash_No._23_1985-12_Newsfield_GB#page/n121/mode/1up/|title=Crash - No. 23 (1985-12)(Newsfield)(GB)|work=archive.org|date=December 1985}}</ref> four out of five stars from ''[[Sinclair User]]'',<ref>{{cite web|url=https://archive.org/stream/sinclair-user-magazine-052/SinclairUser_052_Jul_1986#page/n61/mode/1up/|title=Sinclair User Magazine Issue 052|work=archive.org|date=July 1986}}</ref> 5/10 and 7/10 from ''[[Your Sinclair]]'',<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.zxspectrumreviews.co.uk/review.aspx?gid=5169&rid=9624|title=Sinclair ZX Spectrum Reviews|work=zxspectrumreviews.co.uk}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.zxspectrumreviews.co.uk/review.aspx?gid=5169&rid=9731|title=Sinclair ZX Spectrum Reviews|work=zxspectrumreviews.co.uk}}</ref> and 60% from ''[[Zzap!64]]''.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gamebase64.com/oldsite/gameofweek/12/gotw_snowqueen.htm|title=gamebase64.com - The Gamebase Collection|work=gamebase64.com}}</ref>

